      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": "# Question 4: \nWrite a program to search an integer from a given list of integers \nInput\n    An array a of n integers\n    An integer x\nOutput\n    An index i such that a[i] = x, if i exists\n    -1, otherwise \n",
      "metadata": {
        "language": "markdown",
        "id": "9404ac8b-0220-4b2c-9de7-96336024c644"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "8029f3a8-1211-4331-b694-962bc58e184e",
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": "void find_index(int[] numbers, int n){\r\n    int result = -1;\r\n    for (int i=0; i<numbers.length; i++){\r\n        if (numbers[i]== n){\r\n            result = i;\r\n        };\r\n    };\r\n    IO.println(result);\r\n};\r\n\r\nint[] lst = {1,3,5,6,7,9};\r\nint[] lst2 ={};\r\nfind_index(lst2, 2);\r\nfind_index(lst, 3);",
      "metadata": {
        "language": "java",
        "id": "8029f3a8-1211-4331-b694-962bc58e184e",
        "executionSummary": {
          "executionOrder": 59,
          "success": true
        }
      },
      "execution_count": 59,
      "outputs": [
        {
          "output_type": "execute_result",
          "data": {
            "text/plain": "-1\r\n1\r\n"
          },
